(21, '', 'Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G with 6.67? FHD+ 120Hz AMOLED display, Snapdragon 695, 5000mAh battery and Remi ', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355654&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Redmi-Note-11-Pro-5G.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;572&quot; height=&quot;532&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Xiaomi today introduced the Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G, the company’s latest 5G smartphone for the global markets, as well as Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G model. Both the phones pack a 6.67? FHD+ 120Hz AMOLED DotDisplay with a 16MP camera inside the punch-hole. These feature a 108MP rear camera, 8MP ultra-wide and a 2MP macro camera. The Note 11 Pro features an additional 2MP depth sensor.&lt;span id=&quot;more-355651&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355653&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Redmi-Note-11-Pro-and-Pro-5G-features-1024x512.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;287&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Redmi Note 11 Pro is powered by Helio G96 SoC and the 5G model is powered by Snapdragon 695 SoC, with support for liquid cooling. Both these feature a side-mounted fingerprint scanner and pack a 5000mAh battery with support for 67W turbo charging that can charge up to 50% in 15 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355655&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Redmi-Note-11-Pro.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;478&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G and Redmi Note 11 Pro specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;6.67-inch FHD+ (1080×2400 pixels) AMOLED display with 120Hz refresh rate, DCI-P3 color gamut, 1200nits peak brightness&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G – Octa Core Snapdragon 695 8nm Mobile Platform (2.2GHz x 2+1.8GHz x 6 Kryo 560 CPUs) with Adreno 619L GPU&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Redmi Note 11 Pro – Octa Core MediaTek Helio G96 12nm processor (Dual 2.05GHz A76 + Hexa 2GHz A55 CPUs) with Mali-G57 MC2 GPU&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;6GB LPDDR4X RAM with 64GB UFS 2.2 internal storage, 6GB / 8GB LPDDR4X RAM with 128GB UFS 2.2 internal storage, expandable memory up to 1TB with microSD&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Android 11 with MIUI 13&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hybrid SIM (nano + nano / microSD)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;108MP rear primary camera with Samsung HM2 sensor, f/1.9 aperture, 8MP 118° ultra-wide angle camera, 2MP macro camera with f/2.4 aperture, 2MP depth sensor with f/2.4 aperture (Redmi Note 11 Pro only)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;16MP front camera with f/2.4 aperture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Side-mounted fingerprint sensor, IR blaster&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3.5mm audio jack, Stereo speakers, Hi-Res Audio certification&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 164.19 x 76.1 x 8.12mm; Weight: 202g&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5G SA / NSA (Only in Note 11 Pro 5G), Dual 4G VoLTE, Wi-Fi 802.11 ac (2.4GHz + 5GHz), Bluetooth 5.1, GPS + GLONASS, USB Type-C, NFC&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5000mAh (typical) battery with 67W fast charging&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Redmi Note 11 Pro comes in Graphite Gray, Polar White and Star Blue colors and is priced at $299 (Rs. 22,395 approx.) for 6GB+64GB, $329 (Rs. 24,640 approx.) for 6GB+128GB and $349 (Rs. 26,140 approx.) for 8GB + 128GB models.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G comes in Graphite Gray, Polar White and Atlantic Blue colors and is priced at $329 (Rs. 24,640 approx.) for 6GB+64GB, $349 (Rs. 26,140 approx.) for 6GB+128GB and $379 (Rs. 28,385 approx.) for 8GB + 128GB models.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Early bird pricing is $279 and $299 for the 6GB + 64GB models, respectively, when they go on sale on February 16th and 17th on Aliexpress.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_355651&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /1044778/300x250 --&gt;&lt;div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\' style=\'height:250px; width:300px;margin-left:30px;\'&gt;&lt;script type=\'text/javascript\'&gt;\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\'); });\n&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-info&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-avatar&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-avatar --&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-description&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;author-title&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-heading&quot;&gt;Author:&lt;/span&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;author-bio&quot;&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar is a Mobile Technology Enthusiast who is passionate about Mobile phones and Mobile apps. He uses the phones he reviews as his main phone. You can follow him on  &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://instagram.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;author-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/author/srivatsan&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot;&gt; View all posts by Srivatsan Sridhar			&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!-- .author-bio --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-description --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-info --&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Redmi-Note-11-Pro-5G.jpg', '', 'Redmi-Note-11-Pro-5G-with-6-67-FHD-120Hz-AMOLED-display-Snapdragon-695-5000mAh-battery-and-Remi-Note-11-Pro-announced', 'draft', 'Redmi Note 11 Pro 5G with 6.67? FHD+ 120Hz AMOLED display, Snapdragon 695, 5000mAh battery and Remi Note 11 Pro announced', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:12:40'),
(22, '', 'ESET Smart Security Premium	Review', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355634&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;378&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ESET, popular for its antivirus and firewall products, released the latest version of Smart Security Premium that offers ultimate protection for Windows, macOS and Android. In addition to Malware, ransomware and phishing protection as well as network and smart device protection that is found in the ESET Internet Security, the ESET Smart Security Premium also offers Privacy and banking protection, Sensitive data encryption, Password management and Protection against new threats. Let us dive into the review to find out what it has to offer.&lt;span id=&quot;more-355627&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ESET NOD32 Antivirus, ESET Internet Security and ESET Smart&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Premium features compared&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;aligncenter wp-image-355632&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium-vs-Internet-Security-vs-Antivirus-652x1024.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;902&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As you can see from the table, the ESET Smart Security Premium is feature-packed. The offline updates and remote management features are only available in business editions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355637&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-12.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;572&quot; height=&quot;397&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The ESET Smart Security Premium  version 15 added LiveGuard for cloud analysis of suspect files, Windows 11 support, added option to use QR codes to associate with ESET HOME (formerly myESET), added social nmedia sign-ins for ESET HOME and other improvements and bug fixes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ESET says that the Smart Security Premium uses Advanced Machine Learning, DNA Detections and a cloud-based reputation system developed in 13 R&amp;D centers. Let use check out how it is in the review.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355636&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-13.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;400&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The user interface is simple, and shows all the important details in the sidebar including Home, Computer scan, Update, Tools, Setup and the  Online Help is now integrated into ESET Smart Security Premium and offers dynamically updated support content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355646&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;399&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The software proactively detects and cleans more known and unknown viruses, worms, trojans and rootkits. Advanced heuristics flags even never-before-seen malware, protecting you from unknown threats and neutralizing them before they can do any harm, says the company. The scanning takes a lot of time if you have an old machine, and there is no quick scan option that is found in most antivirus apps.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355644&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-5-1024x539.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;572&quot; height=&quot;301&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Web access protection and Anti-Phishing works by monitoring communication between web browsers and remote servers (including SSL). Email client protection provides control of email communication received through the POP3(S) and IMAP(S) protocols. It blocked a website that had an issue with the certificate.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;size-full wp-image-355645 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-4.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;426&quot; height=&quot;246&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It also removed an adware threat in JavaScript on a website.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355647&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;399&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The company keeps pushing regular updates to update the detection engine to ensure the maximum level of security. It automatically scans all USB flash drives, memory cards and CDs/DVDs for threats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355648&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;573&quot; height=&quot;400&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can enable additional security tools that includes a password manager, secure data that encrypts data on computer and USB drives, parental control and anti-theft feature.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355639&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-10.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;571&quot; height=&quot;399&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The password manager that protects and stores your passwords and personal data across browsers and devices including Android and macOS, in addition to Windows, and also has two-factor authentication.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355635&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-14-1024x545.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;305&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Banking &amp; Payment protection provides a secured browser for use when accessing online banking or online payment gateways to ensure all online transactions take place in a trusted and secure environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355642&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-7.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;397&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Intelligent Firewall prevents unauthorized users from accessing your computer and taking advantage of your personal data. ESET Antispam protection serves to protect against Spam.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355640&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-9.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;401&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Liveguard discovers and stops never-before-seen threats and processes information for future detection. There is a dedicated gamer mode that can Postpones all pop-up windows, updates or other system-intensive activities to conserve system resources for gaming and other full-screen activities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-355638&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium_FoneArena-11-1024x720.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;404&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;One of my favorite feature is Anti-Theft that, when activated, lets you lock your and also find it in case it is stolen. The device will be listed in the web interface that allows you to manage the ESET Anti-Theft configuration and administer anti-theft features. You can also send message, view activity and also check the location, view screenshots and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Overall, the ESET Smart Security Premium offers an all-round protection from all the threats and includes useful features like password manager, Anti-theft and Gamer mode. It is also cross-platform, but I miss VPN service or any cloud storage or backup for the price you pay.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pricing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The ESET Smart Security Premium is priced at Rs. 3,919 for 1 year for one device, and Rs. 4,639 for three devices, but you get 25% discount with 2 years of subscription. You can check it out on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.eset.com/in/online-store/#home-all-products&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;eset.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Excellent malware protection&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All-in-one protection for Windows, macOS, and Android&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Useful Anti-theft and Gamer mode&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in password manager with cross-platform sync&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cons&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Scanning takes time, and no quick scan option&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No VPN, Cloud storage or backup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_355627&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /1044778/300x250 --&gt;&lt;div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\' style=\'height:250px; width:300px;margin-left:30px;\'&gt;&lt;script type=\'text/javascript\'&gt;\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\'); });\n&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-info&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-avatar&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-avatar --&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-description&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;author-title&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-heading&quot;&gt;Author:&lt;/span&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;author-bio&quot;&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar is a Mobile Technology Enthusiast who is passionate about Mobile phones and Mobile apps. He uses the phones he reviews as his main phone. You can follow him on  &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://instagram.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;author-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/author/srivatsan&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot;&gt; View all posts by Srivatsan Sridhar			&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!-- .author-bio --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-description --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-info --&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ESET-Smart-Security-Premium.jpg', '', 'ESET-Smart-Security-Premium-Review', 'draft', 'ESET Smart Security Premium	Review', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:12:40'),
(23, '', 'OnePlus Nord 2T with 6.43-inch FHD+ 90Hz AMOLED display, Dimensity 1300, 80W fast charging surfaces', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-344575&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/OnePlus-Nord-2-5G-colours-1024x472.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;576&quot; height=&quot;266&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;OnePlus &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/344358/oneplus-nord-2-5g-price-india-specifications.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;launched&lt;/a&gt; the Nord 2 smartphone back in July last year, and the Nord 2 x PAC-MAN Edition was launched in November. Now the company is said to be gearing up to launch the Nord 2T as an upgrade to the Nord 2 soon. We still don’t have the render of the phone yet, but the specifications of the phone has surfaced, thanks to @OnLeaks.&lt;span id=&quot;more-355628&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;According to rumours, the Nord 2T is expected to be powered by Dimensity 1300, successor to Dimensity 1200 SoC and bring the 80W fast charging that was first introduced in the OnePlus 10 Pro, while retaining most specifications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OnePlus Nord 2T rumored specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;6.43-inch Full HD+ Fluid AMOLED display with 90Hz refresh rate&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Octa Core MediaTek Dimensity 1300 processor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;6GB / 8GB LPDDR4X RAM with 128GB (UFS 3.1) storage, 12GB LPDDR4X RAM with 256GB (UFS 3.1) storage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Android 12 with OxygenOS 12&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dual SIM (nano + nano)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;50MP rear camera with LED flash, OIS, 8MP ultra-wide camera, 2MP mono camera&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;32MP front-facing camera&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In-display fingerprint sensor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;USB Type-C audio, Stereo speakers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5G SA /NSA, Dual 4G VoLTE, Wi-Fi 6 802.11 ax (2.4GHz + 5GHz) 2X2 MIMO, Bluetooth 5.2, GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, Beidou, NavIC, NFC, USB Type-C&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;4500mAh battery with 80W Fast Charging&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is not clear when the OnePlus is planning to launch the Nord 2T in India, but the company is said to launch a new Nord smartphone in the country in February.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.digit.in/news/mobile-phones/exclusive-oneplus-nord-2t-key-specs-leak-62680.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_355628&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /1044778/300x250 --&gt;&lt;div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\' style=\'height:250px; width:300px;margin-left:30px;\'&gt;&lt;script type=\'text/javascript\'&gt;\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\'); });\n&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-info&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-avatar&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-avatar --&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-description&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;author-title&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-heading&quot;&gt;Author:&lt;/span&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;author-bio&quot;&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar is a Mobile Technology Enthusiast who is passionate about Mobile phones and Mobile apps. He uses the phones he reviews as his main phone. You can follow him on  &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://instagram.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;author-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/author/srivatsan&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot;&gt; View all posts by Srivatsan Sridhar			&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!-- .author-bio --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-description --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-info --&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/OnePlus-Nord-2-5G-colours-1024x472.jpg', '', 'OnePlus-Nord-2T-with-6-43-inch-FHD-90Hz-AMOLED-display-Dimensity-1300-80W-fast-charging-surfaces', 'draft', 'OnePlus Nord 2T with 6.43-inch FHD+ 90Hz AMOLED display, Dimensity 1300, 80W fast charging surfaces', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:12:40'),
(24, '', 'realme Android 12 (realme UI 3.0) Update Tracker [Update: realme Pad will get Android 12 in Q3, 2022', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;aligncenter wp-image-350225&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/realme-UI-3.0.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;575&quot; height=&quot;327&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;realme &lt;a title=&quot;realme UI 3.0 based on Android 12 unveiled &amp;mdash; Early access begins this October&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/350223/realme-ui-3-0-android-12-features.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; the realme UI 3.0, based on Android 12, a couple of months back. realmeUI 3.0 come with a Fluid Space Design, More Spatial Layout, and More Expressive UI experience. It also includes 3D icon, Omoji, AOD Personalizations, AI Smooth Engine, Floating window 2.0, Security and Privacy Features, Phone Manager 2.0, and App permission Recording.&lt;span id=&quot;more-353421&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;realme has already shared the list of smartphones eligible to receive the realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) update. This post will help our readers in keeping a track of Android 12 Update for realme devices.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;realme Devices that have received Android 12 based realme UI 3.0 Update&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme GT [Stable]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme X7 Max [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme GT NEO 2 [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/337349/realme-8-pro-realme-ui-2-0-software-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;realme 8 Pro&lt;/a&gt; [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/352725/realme-gt-master-edition-realme-ui-3-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;realme GT Master Edition&lt;/a&gt; [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/337133/realme-8-realme-ui-2-0-software-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;realme 8&lt;/a&gt; [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/311285/realme-x50-pro-realme-ui-2-0-software-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;realme X50 Pro 5G&lt;/a&gt; [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/321909/realme-7-pro-realme-ui-2-0-software-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;realme 7 Pro&lt;/a&gt; [Early Access]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;realme Devices that will receive Android 12 based realme UI 3.0 Update&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Feb 2022&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme X7 Pro 5G&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme C25&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;March 2022&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme C25s&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme narzo 50A&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme narzo 30&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme 7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme 8i&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Q2, 2022&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme X7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme X3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme X3 SuperZoom&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme 8 5G&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme 8s&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme 7 5G&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme narzo 30 Pro 5G&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme narzo 30 5G&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Q3, 2022&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;realme Pad&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 25, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme Pad&lt;/strong&gt; will receive Android 12 update in Q3 2022, &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1486218031158874112&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;confirms&lt;/a&gt; realme.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 25, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme 7 Pro&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1485832340319064064&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme 7 Pro users running firmware version RMX2170_11_C.28 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme  7 Pro Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Read the following disclaimers provided by the company before applying for the Early Access program,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;• Please make sure your phone is not rooted. • To prevent data loss, please backup your personal data before proceeding. • Some third-party application versions might not be compatible with Android 12 yet, after updating these applications might not be available or crash on your device.Therefore, it is recommended to update all your applications to the latest version available on the Play Store before your update. • The Early Access versions may have an unpredictable impact on your phone and effect on daily use. • Please ensure that the available phone storage is more than 10 GB. Otherwise there will be a risk of update failure (To check the phone storage head to Settings &gt; Additional Settings &gt; Storage). • Due to unpredictable factors such as network communication and strategy adjustment, it is not possible to guarantee that every applicant will receive the update. In case the update is not received, we suggest you patiently wait for the official release.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 25, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme X50 Pro&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1485832340319064064&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme X50 Pro users running firmware version RMX2076PUNV1B_11_C.23 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme  X50 Pro Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 21, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme 8&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1483695571544944640&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme 8 users running firmware version RMX3085_11_A.24 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme  8 Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 12, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT Master Edition&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program for the users running firmware version RMX3360_11_A.09 is now live in India. Users can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme  GT Master Edition Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Jan 10, 2022]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://static.c.realme.com/IN/wm-thread/1480553092511465472.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;realme has &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1450396427162341376&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; the detailed realme UI 3.0 Early Access program roll out schedule for Q1, 2022.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 31, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT Master Edition&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1476930295277113344&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme GT Master Edition users running firmware version RMX3360_11_A.08 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme  GT Master Edition Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 29, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) stable update is now &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1476068178592301056&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;rolling out&lt;/a&gt; in India. The update comes with firmware version &lt;strong&gt;RMX2202_11_C.05&lt;/strong&gt;. Check out realme GT Android 12 update changelog below,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New design&lt;/strong&gt; • The all-new design, which emphasizes a sense of space, deliver a simple, clean, and comfortable visual and interactive experience. • Revamps the page layout based on the principle of reducing visual noise and spacing out elements, and prioritizes information with different colors to make key information stand out. • Redesigns icons using new materials to give more depth and a greater sense of space and texture to the icons. • Optimizes Quantum Animation Engine: Quantum Animation Engine 3.0 implements the concept of mass to make animations more lifelike, and optimizes more than 300 animations to bring a more natural user experience. • More creative Always-On Display: Adds realmeow and Portrait silhouette to let you freely express yourself. &lt;strong&gt;Convenience &amp; efficiency&lt;/strong&gt; • FlexDrop is renamed Flexible Windows and is optimized: • Optimizes the method of switching floating windows between different sizes. • You can now drag a file from My Files or a photo from the Photos app to a floating window. &lt;strong&gt;Performance&lt;/strong&gt; • Adds Quick launch, a feature that detects the apps you use frequently and pre-loads them so you can open them quickly. • Adds a chart to display your battery usage. • Improves the responsiveness of turning on or off WiFi, Bluetooth, Airplane mode, and NFC. &lt;strong&gt;Games&lt;/strong&gt; • In team fight scenes, games run more smoothly at a stable frame rate. • Reduces the CPU load average and lowers the battery usage. &lt;strong&gt;Camera&lt;/strong&gt; • You can now decide which camera modes are displayed on the menu bar and in what order they are displayed. • You can now drag the zoom slider to zoom in or out smoothly when shooting a video using the rear camera. &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; • Optimizes the auto brightness algorithm to adapt screen brightness to more scenes for a comfortable screen reading experience. &lt;strong&gt;Accessibility&lt;/strong&gt; • Optimizes accessibility: • Adds visuals to text instructions for an intuitive understanding of accessibility functions. • Optimizes categorization of functions by grouping them into vision, hearing, interactive actions, and general. • TalkBack supports more system apps including Photos, Phone, Mail, and Calendar..&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 28, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT Neo 2T&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 Early Access program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.realmebbs.com/post-details/1475637381033250816&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in China.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 23, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Stable update is now &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.realmebbs.com/post-details/1473549530586116096&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;rolling out&lt;/a&gt; in China.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 17, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme 8 Pro&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has been announced in India. realme 8 Pro users running firmware version RMX3081_11_C.09 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme 8 Pro Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 16, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT Neo 2&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has now been announced in India. realme GT Neo 2 users running firmware version RMX2202_11_C.04 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details &lt;/em&gt;to apply for realme GT Neo 2 Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 16, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT Master Explorer Edition&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Open Beta program has been &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.realmebbs.com/post-details/1471374570383867904&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in China.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 10, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has now been announced in India. realme GT Neo 2 users running firmware version RMX3370_11_A.05 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details ? Apply Now &lt;/em&gt;to apply for realme GT Neo 2 Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Dec 10, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme X7 Max&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has now been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1469203311998595072&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme X7 Max users running firmware version RMX3031_11_A.21 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Apply Now&lt;/em&gt; to apply for the realme X7 Max realme UI 3.0 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;[Oct 19, 2021]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;realme GT&lt;/strong&gt; realme UI 3.0 (Android 12) Early Access program has now been announced in India. realme GT users running firmware version RMX2202_11_A.14 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Apply Now ? Submit your details and finish the quiz &lt;/em&gt;to apply for realme GT Android 12 Early Access program.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_353421&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/realme-UI-3.0.jpg', '', 'realme-Android-12-realme-UI-3-0-Update-Tracker-Update-realme-Pad-will-get-Android-12-in-Q3-2022-', 'draft', 'realme Android 12 (realme UI 3.0) Update Tracker [Update: realme Pad will get Android 12 in Q3, 2022]', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:12:40'),
(25, '', 'realme Pad will not get Android 12 update [Update: It is coming in Q3 2022 after all]', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/realme-Pad.jpg&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;502&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Update: January 26, 2022 – After severe backlash, realme has backtracked from its earlier statement and has confirmed that it will offer Android 12 update for the realme Pad in Q3 2022, which is between July and September. The company has also promised 3 years of security update for the tablet. It has also removed the realme Pad question from the Q&amp;A it posted earlier.&lt;span id=&quot;more-354998&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Earlier: realme &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/348247/realme-pad-price-india-specifications.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;launched&lt;/a&gt; the realme Pad, the company’s first tablet running realme UI for Pad based on Android 11 in September last year. This week in the realme Community FAQ, the company has confirmed that the realme Pad will not be updated to Android 12. The company said that it will continue to get security and performance updates throughout its software lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;HMD Global launched the Nokia T20 tablet in India in November running Android 11. At the launch, it confirmed that the tablet will receive 2 years of OS updates and 3 years of security updates.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Even Samsung has &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/352092/samsung-android-12-update-list-one-ui-4-0-india.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;confirmed&lt;/a&gt; Android 12 update to its budget Galaxy Tab A7 (2020) and Galaxy Tab A7 Lite, in addition to its S series.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We expected realme to offer at least one major update for the tablet, but it looks like the company will offer updates &lt;a title=&quot;realme Android 12 (realme UI 3.0) Update Tracker [Update: Detailed realme UI 3.0 Early Access Program Schedule Announced for Q1 2022]&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/353421/realme-android-12-realme-ui-3-0-update-tracker.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;only for its smartphones&lt;/a&gt;, and not the tablet. Hope we can expect realme to offer at least one Android update for its second generation realme Pad that is expected to release later this year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1480403204557537280&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_354998&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /1044778/300x250 --&gt;&lt;div id=\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\' style=\'height:250px; width:300px;margin-left:30px;\'&gt;&lt;script type=\'text/javascript\'&gt;\ngoogletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display(\'div-gpt-ad-1466626458146-0\'); });\n&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-info&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-avatar&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-avatar --&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;author-description&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;author-title&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;author-heading&quot;&gt;Author:&lt;/span&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;author-bio&quot;&gt; Srivatsan Sridhar is a Mobile Technology Enthusiast who is passionate about Mobile phones and Mobile apps. He uses the phones he reviews as his main phone. You can follow him on  &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://instagram.com/ssrivatsan&quot;&gt;Instagram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;author-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/author/srivatsan&quot; rel=&quot;author&quot;&gt; View all posts by Srivatsan Sridhar			&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!-- .author-bio --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-description --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .author-info --&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/realme-Pad.jpg', '', 'realme-Pad-will-not-get-Android-12-update-Update-It-is-coming-in-Q3-2022-after-all-', 'draft', 'realme Pad will not get Android 12 update [Update: It is coming in Q3 2022 after all]', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:12:40');
