(49, '', 'Just Corseca Ray K’anabis smartwatch with Bluetooth calling launched for Rs. 8,999', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/10-1024x1024.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;574&quot; height=&quot;574&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Just Corseca, a consumer electronic company, has launched a new salt-water resistant smartwatch – Ray K’anabis. With this device, the company targets athletes, hikers, and others.&lt;span id=&quot;more-355449&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The smartwatch features a unibody design that can be inundated in water to 1.5 meters for half an hour, claims the company. The device can display the sports data, view your pace, distance, as well as your exercise route map.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The watch also comes with features like music control, camera control, find my phone, and others.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Just Corseca Ray K’anabis specification&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;1.28-inch Full HD IPS 240×240 pixel resolution&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hi-Fi calling function&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blood pressure, Blood saturation tracker, Heart rate monitor, Menstrual cycle, Drink water reminder, and dedicated Multiple Sports modes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in microphone and speaker&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;400mAh lithium polymer battery (10-15 days of normal usage, and 20 days of standby time.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Available in two colors — Black and Green, Just Corseca Ray K’anabis is priced at Rs. 8,999 and available for purchase at all &lt;a href=&quot;https://amzn.to/3qOKR8m&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;online&lt;/a&gt; and offline stores.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Commenting on the launch, Ritesh Goenka, Group MD, Just Corseca, said:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;The smartwatch industry is fast-paced and registering a growth of 110 per cent YoY in 2021, And, Just Corseca aspires to be in the top league. With this new range of smartwatches, we are confident of yet again meeting the customers’ expectations and replicating the success story in the Indian market. The product would have the same functionality as a standard Just Corseca watch but with extra salt-water resistance. The latest Just Corseca watch models are salt-water resistant to 1.5 meters for half an hour.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_355449&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/10-1024x1024.jpg', '', 'Just-Corseca-Ray-K-anabis-smartwatch-with-Bluetooth-calling-launched-for-Rs-8-999', 'draft', 'Just Corseca Ray K’anabis smartwatch with Bluetooth calling launched for Rs. 8,999', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:13:30'),
(50, '', 'realme X3 and X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Software Update Tracker [C.11 Update with January 2022 Andr', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&quot;lazy&quot; class=&quot;aligncenter wp-image-319834&quot; src=&quot;https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/realme-X3-SuperZoom-review-fonearena-10-1024x576.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;573&quot; height=&quot;323&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;realme &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/315975/realme-x3-x3-superzoom-price-india-specifications.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;launched&lt;/a&gt; realme X3 Series back in June 2020 in India. These smartphones run on &lt;strong&gt;Android 11 based realme UI 2.0&lt;/strong&gt;. The realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom are confirmed to get Android 12 based realme UI 3.0 update.&lt;span id=&quot;more-319046&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;realme doesn’t follow a fixed update frequency, but the company rolls out updates frequently. This post will help our readers in keeping track of realme UI updates for realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom (RMX2081PU). Also, check out our realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom content,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/319619/realme-x3-superzoom-review.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;realme X3 SuperZoom Review — It’s all about the optics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/292648/how-to-uninstall-apps-realme-without-root.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;How to uninstall apps on realme X3 without root&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/292648/how-to-uninstall-apps-realme-without-root.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;How to uninstall apps on realme X3 SuperZoom without root&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note that realme follows staged roll-out and the updates are randomly pushed to a limited number of users and a broader roll-out usually takes a few days after the company makes sure there are no critical bugs.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 3.0 Updates,&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Oct 13, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 3.0 Early Access update, based on Android 12, will be rolled out in Q2 2022, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/350223/realme-ui-3-0-android-12-features.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;confirms&lt;/a&gt; realme.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Updates,&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Jan 21, 2022]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom RMX2081_11_C.11 update is now rolling out in India. The update weighs 685MBs in size and brings January 2022 Android security patch to the devices. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Integrates the December 2021 and January 2022 Android security patches. &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Improves system stability and performance.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Nov 13, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom C.10 update is now rolling out in India. The update weighs 304MBs in size and brings November 2021 Android security patch to the devices. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Integrates the October and November 2021 Android security patches. &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Improves system stability and performance.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Sep 27, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom C.09 update is now rolling out in India. The update brings September 2021 Android security patch to the devices. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Integrates the August and September 2021 Android security patches. &lt;strong&gt;Languages&lt;/strong&gt; ? Adds support for Estonian and Lithuanian. &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Improves system stability and performance. &lt;strong&gt;Apps&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixes an issue that might cause an error to occur when you are saving a video on Instagram Stories.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[June 26, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom C.07 update is now rolling out in India. The update brings June 2021 Android security patch to the devices. &lt;pre&gt;? Integrates the May and June 2021 Android security patches. ? Adds the Hot Apps folder to the Home screen. ? Improves system stability. ? Fixes an issue where the OSIE visual effect would not take effect in some apps. ? Fixes an issue where &quot;Portrait distortion correction&quot; would not take effect when you take a selfie. ? Reduces audio latency when you play certain games using realme earphones. ? Optimizes the Wi-Fi scan feature in Recovery mode.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[May 25, 2021]: r&lt;strong&gt;ealme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Stable&lt;/strong&gt; update, based on Android 11, is now rolling out in India. The OTA comes with firmware version RMX2081_11_C.06 and weighs 668MBs for those who were using realme UI 2.0 Beta. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personalizations&lt;/strong&gt; Personalize the user interface to make it your own ? You can now create your own wallpaper by picking colors from your photos. ? Third-party icons for apps on the home screen are now supported. ? Three Dark mode styles are available: Enhanced, medium, and gentle; wallpapers and icons can be adjusted to Dark mode; and the display contrast can be adjusted automatically to ambient light. &lt;strong&gt;High Efficiency&lt;/strong&gt; ? You can now drag text, images, or files out of a floating window or from one app to another app in Split screen mode. ? Optimized the editing page of Smart Sidebar: Two tabs are displayed and the order of items can be customized. &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added &quot;Tone tunes&quot;: Consecutive notification tones will be linked to form a single melody. ? You can now determine a time period when Do Not Disturb is on. ? Added weather animations to provide you with a more interesting experience. ? Optimized vibration effects for text input and gameplay. ? Optimized &quot;Auto brightness&quot;. &lt;strong&gt;Launcher&lt;/strong&gt; ? You can now remove a folder or combine it with another one. ? Added filters for &quot;Drawer mode&quot;: You can now filter apps by letters, install time, or usage frequency to quickly find an app. &lt;strong&gt;Security and Privacy&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added &quot;System cloner&quot;: You can create a system clone from your main system and use different fingerprints to enter different systems. ? You can now turn &quot;App lock&quot; on or off in Quick Settings. ? More powerful SOS functions Emergency info: You can quickly display your personal emergency info to first responders. The information can be shown even when your screen is locked. ? Optimized &quot;Permission manager&quot;: You can now choose &quot;Allow only once&quot; for sensitive permissions to better protect your privacy. &lt;strong&gt;Games&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added Immersive mode which reduces disturbances while gaming so you can stay focused. ? You can change the way to summon Game Assistant. &lt;strong&gt;Communications&lt;/strong&gt; ? You can share your personal hotspot with others via a QR code. &lt;strong&gt;Photos&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added the Cloud Sync for Private Safe feature which allows you to sync the photos in your Private Safe to the cloud. ? Optimized the photo editing feature with upgraded algorithms and more markup effects and filters. &lt;strong&gt;HeyTap Cloud&lt;/strong&gt; ? You can back up your photos, documents, system settings, WeChat data, and more, and easily migrate to a new phone. ? You can select the types of data to be backed up or restored. &lt;strong&gt;Camera&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added shortcuts to instantly share and edit photos or videos you just took. ? Added the inertial zoom feature which makes zooming smoother during video shooting. ? Added the level and grid feature to help you compose videos. &lt;strong&gt;realme Lab&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added Sleep Capsule, help you schedule downtime and secure your sleep time &lt;strong&gt;Accessibility&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added &quot;Sound amplifier&quot;: You can amplify faint sounds in the environment and soften loud sounds when wearing earphones.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Apr 20, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Open Beta program now been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1384390438852595712&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom users running firmware version A.51 or A.53 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom Android 11 Open Beta program.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Feb 24, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Open Early Access program applications are once again &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1364500418293448704&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;opened&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom users running firmware version A.47 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom Android 11 Early Access program.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Jan 30, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Open Early Access program now been &lt;a href=&quot;https://c.realme.com/in/post-details/1355144585080209408&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;announced&lt;/a&gt; in India. realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom users running firmware version A.47 can head over to &lt;em&gt;Settings ? Software Update ? Tap on the settings icon in the top right corner ? Trial Version ? Submit your details&lt;/em&gt; to apply for realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom Android 11 Early Access program.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Sep 21, 2020]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom will be upgraded to &lt;strong&gt;Android 11 based realme UI&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;2.0&lt;/strong&gt; in Jan 2021, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/323587/realme-ui-2-android-11-update-devices-schedule.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;confirms&lt;/a&gt; realme.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom realme UI 1.0 Updates,&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Mar 16, 2021]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11.A.51 with February and March security patch. It also improves system performance adds new FinShell Pay app, brings new Screenshot features and more. &lt;pre&gt;Security ? Updated Android security patch: February &amp; March,2021 Application ? Added FinShell Pay System ? Optimized system performance and improved system stability Screenshot ? Optimized the crop response time after screenshoting ? Optimized the operating interface in croping screenshot ? Fixed the probabilistic cannot save screenshot issue after editing screenshot Clock ? Fixed the lagging issue when long screenshoting in adding world clock interface&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Feb 7, 2021]: realme X3 and realme X3 SuperZoom A.49 update is now rolling out in India. The update brings January 2021 Android security patch to the devices. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Updated Android security patch: Jan, 2021 &lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic issue that reconnecting the Bluetooth headset during a call caused loud sound &lt;strong&gt;Clone Phone&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic issue that data migration failure &lt;strong&gt;Recording&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic issue that Recording displays abnormally when the recording file is deleted &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized system performance and improved system stability&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Dec 16, 2020]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11_A.47 with December Android security patch. The update adds a new icon for phone calls with Bluetooth earphones. Along with this, the update also brings the feature to turn off the flashlight with the power button when the screen is off. Apart from it, the company has also optimized the experience for the fingerprint and face unlock combination. realme has also fixed several bugs related to dark mode, alarm, and photos. &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Updated Android security patch: Dec, 2020 &lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added a new icon for phone calls with Bluetooth earphone &lt;strong&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized the experience when using the combination of fingerprint and face to unlock &lt;strong&gt;Photos&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic screen flicker when editing the album &lt;strong&gt;Alarm&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic crashing issue in alarm detail interface &lt;strong&gt;Dark Mode&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic screen flicker when entering passwords entries in Dark mode ? Fixed when using Clone Phone in Dark mode, the probabilistic issue that From Sunset to Sunrise status is out of sync&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Nov 9, 2020]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11_A.45 with October Android security patch. The update adds multiple new toggles such as toggle for system icons in the status bar, Sunset to Sunrise toggle for eye comfort, and toggle for display keyboard when entering app drawer.  Apart from it, the update also brings an optimized display effect for the screen brightness lock, fixes the network connect loss which users encountered in certain scenarios, along with probabilistic time display issue, and probabilistic lagging issue with the use of Instagram to switch video. [&lt;a href=&quot;https://download.c.realme.com/osupdate/RMX2081PU_11_OTA_0450_all_e54LC7DmCgBX.ozip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Download Link&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Android security patch: October, 2020 &lt;strong&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added toggle for system icons in Status bar ? Added From Sunset to Sunrise toggle for eye comfort ? Added toggle for display keyboard when entering app drawer &lt;strong&gt;Game Space&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized the display effect of the screen brightness lock &lt;strong&gt;Network&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the network connection loss in some scenarios &lt;strong&gt;Album&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic screen flicker when entering the album &lt;strong&gt;Status bar&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic time display issue &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic Lagging issue with use of Instagram to switch video&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Sep 29, 2020]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11_A.43 with September Android security patch. The update weighs just 381MBs in size, and brings &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fonearena.com/blog/310399/soloop-video-editing-app-realme-download.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Soloop&lt;/a&gt; video editing app to smartphones, along with several bug fixes. [&lt;a href=&quot;https://download.c.realme.com/osupdate/RMX2081PU_11_OTA_0430_all_0peGeINpSpOG.ozip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Download Link&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Updated Android security patch: September, 2020 &lt;strong&gt;Applications&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added Soloop &lt;strong&gt;File Manager&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic crashing issue when renaming &lt;strong&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the display issue of the battery icon in the status bar while switching to Super power saving mode ? Fixed the probabilistic issue of unable to turn down the brightness after turning on the Power saving mode  &lt;strong&gt;Multi-user&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the missing prompt window when swiping upward to exit in horizontal-screen games &lt;strong&gt;Gaming&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the noise issue in Marvel Contest of Champion &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic restart issue caused by network stuck ? Fixed the probabilistic noise issue of Whatsapp when playing voice messages in the background ? Fixed the probabilistic issue that the fingerprint pattern is displayed when using Face unlock to enter the locked apps&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Aug 31, 2020]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11_A.41 update with August Android security patch. The update brings super nighttime standby feature which can be found under realme Lab section. A.41 update also brings auto scroll for scrolling screenshots along with multi-user feature and Super power saving mode. [&lt;a href=&quot;https://download.c.realme.com/osupdate/RMX2081PU_11_OTA_0410_all_zwP3AZihp1fj.ozip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Download Link&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt; ? Android Security Patch: August, 2020 &lt;strong&gt;realme Lab&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added the Super nighttime standby feature &lt;strong&gt;Screenshot&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added auto scroll feature in scrolling screenshot &lt;strong&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added Super Power Saving Mode ? Added Icon Pull-down gesture feature in launcher settings ? Added return button in the screenshot preview interface ? Added Multi-user feature ? Added Quick guide feature in the battery setting interface ? Added Quick guide feature in the security support interface ? Added Quick guide feature in the other settings interface ? Added automatic downloads option for app updates in the Wi-Fi interface ? Optimized status bar viewing, added second display option &lt;strong&gt;Status Bar&lt;/strong&gt; ? Added independent Switch toggles of focus mode ? Optimized viewing for system update prompt pop-up window ? Optimized &quot;Mute-Bell-Vibrate&quot; icon state &lt;strong&gt;System&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the probabilistic connection issue when using Wi-Fi ? Fixed font display issue of charging animation ? Fixed crashing issue when opening hidden apps with access codes&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[Jul 31, 2o20]: realme has started rolling out RMX2081PU_11_A.39 update with July Android security patch. The update brings smooth scrolling (can be found under realme Lab section) and fixes the voice jam issue when connected to Bluetooth headset using LDAC codec. Turning on/off flight mode will not affect Bluetooth status of the device is also a feature that A.39 update brings to devices along with other optimizations. [&lt;a href=&quot;https://download.c.realme.com/osupdate/RMX2081PU_11_OTA_0390_all_gL1IiprDDtA2.ozip&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Download Link&lt;/a&gt;] &lt;pre&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security:&lt;/strong&gt; ? Updated Android Security Patch: July, 2020 &lt;strong&gt;realme Lab: ?&lt;/strong&gt; Added smooth scrolling feature &lt;strong&gt;Status Bar:&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized the time display issue &lt;strong&gt;Settings:&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized the default state of reduce screen brightness switch in power saving mode &lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth:&lt;/strong&gt; ? Fixed the voice jam issue when connected to Bluetooth headset using LDAC codec &lt;strong&gt;System:&lt;/strong&gt; ? Optimized flight mode, Bluetooth status will not be affected after flight mode is turned on ? Optimized the system power consumption&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Spotted a newer software version for realme X3 or realme X3 SuperZoom? Tip us on &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/FoneArena&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;cs-rating pd-rating&quot; id=&quot;pd_rating_holder_1304431_post_319046&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'https://images.fonearena.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/realme-X3-SuperZoom-review-fonearena-10', '', 'realme-X3-and-X3-SuperZoom-realme-UI-2-0-Software-Update-Tracker-C-11-Update-with-January-2022-Android-Security-Patch-', 'draft', 'realme X3 and X3 SuperZoom realme UI 2.0 Software Update Tracker [C.11 Update with January 2022 Android Security Patch]', 1, 28, '2022-01-29 08:13:30');
