(6, 'Micromax IN 1b', 'micromax-phones', 8999, 0, '/Public/assets/images/default.jpg', '&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Buy the brand new Micromax In 1b smartphone that was launched in India on November 03, 2020. In this dual-SIM (GSM and GSM) mobile both Nano-SIM and Nano-SIM cards can be inserted. Measuring around 164.50 mm x 75.80 mm x 8.90 mm (height x width x thickness) and weighing around 188 grams, the Micromax In 1b is easy to carry and use. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can have an immersive viewing experience as the Micromax In 1b comes with a 6.52-inch IPS LCD touchscreen display that has a resolution of 720x1600 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9. Apart from this, the smartphone offers you a smooth and lag-free performance as it is equipped with an octa-core MediaTek Helio G35 processor. Also, you can access multiple apps at the same time without any interruption.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The smartphone from Micromax is based on the Android 10 operating system and comes with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of inbuilt storage. Also, you can expand the inbuilt storage of your phone up to 128GB using a microSD card with a dedicated slot so that you can store all your local files like songs, games, videos, pictures, and more without worrying about space constraints.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Apart from this, the Micromax In 1b mobile is powered by a massive 5000mAh non-removable battery that supports proprietary fast charging and lets you use the phone for a longer period of time without worrying about battery draining.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Speaking about the optics of Micromax In 1b, you get a dual-camera setup on the rear. There is a 13 MP primary camera with f/1.8 aperture and a 2 MP depth sensor with f/2.4 aperture. Also, the rear camera setup has an LED flash and autofocus. While 