(603, 'Xiaomi Redmi Note 10 Pro', 'xiaomi-phones', 15999, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-76254607,imgsize-400,width-270/76254607.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Redmi Note 10 Pro is an upcoming smartphone from Xiaomi that will come with decent specifications and striking features. It is rumored that the phone will be featuring a 6.47 inches AMOLED touchscreen display that might have a resolution of 1080 x 2340 pixels and an aspect ratio of 19.5:9 that will give you an immersive viewing experience. Besides, the phone is speculated to be available in different color options like Midnight Black, Aurora Green, and Glacier White.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The rumored mobile is expected to be powered by Octa-core (2x2.2 GHz Kryo 470 Gold &amp; 6x1.8 GHz Kryo 470 Silver) Qualcomm SDM730 Snapdragon 730G (8 nm) processor that would provide you a lag-free performance while playing intense graphics games, browsing the web, accessing multiple apps, and doing other things on the phone. In addition to this, Redmi Note 10 Pro might come with a RAM capacity of 8GB and 256GB of internal storage. Hence, you will be able to switch easily between multiple apps and easily store your files of songs, videos, games, and more without any space constraints.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Redmi Note 10 Pro is speculated to come with a multi-camera setup on the rear that would let you click some amazing pictures and record high quality videos. There is expected to be a 108 MP camera with f/1.7 aperture, a 12 MP telephoto lens with f/2.0 aperture, an 8MP telephoto lens with f/2.0 aperture, a 20 MP ultrawide camera with f/2.2 aperture, and a 2 MP macro lens with f/2.4 aperture. Also, there will be different features like auto flash, digital zoom, face detection, touch 