(611, 'Xiaomi Redmi Note 7 Pro', 'xiaomi-phones', 13999, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-67484173,imgsize-400,width-270/67484173.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;Buy the Xiaomi Redmi Note 7 Pro, which not just has pleasant looks but is also equipped with striking features. The mobile phone was launched in India on March 13, 2019 (Official) at a starting price of Rs 13,999.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;This Xiaomi phone is powerful to the core as it lets you enjoy a breezy-smooth performance while accessing multiple apps since it is powered with Octa core (2 GHz, Dual core, Kryo 460 + 1.7 GHz, Hexa Core, Kryo 460) Qualcomm Snapdragon 675. Moreover, the phone comes with 4 GB of RAM and 64 GB of internal storage so that you can store all your songs, videos, games, pictures and other stuff without worrying about space constraints.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The &amp;lt;a href=https://www.gadgetsnow.com/mobile-phones&amp;gt;mobile&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; paves the way for crystal clear visuals as it comes with a 6.3 inches (16 cm) display that has a resolution of 1080 x 2340 pixels..&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Furthermore, the aspect ratio of the Xiaomi Redmi Note 7 Pro is 19.5:9 so that you can enjoy vivid and crystal clear visuals while watching videos, playing games, or streaming movies online..&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The camera specifications of the phone are very captivating. The Xiaomi Redmi Note 7 Pro comes with a Single camera setup on the rear which has 48 MP + 5 MP cameras so that you can capture portraits, landscapes, and more in the form of beautiful pictures. Features on the rear camera setup include Digital Zoom, Auto Flash, Face detection, Touch to focus. On the front, the mobile features a 13 MP camera so that you can click some amazing selfies and do video chats.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/