(613, 'Apple iPhone 13', 'apple-phones', 79900, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-79058673,imgsize-400,width-270/79058673.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Apple has launched the iPhone 13 in different storage variants along with iPhone 13 mini, iPhone 13 Pro, and iPhone 13 Pro Max that come with impressive features and specifications. iPhone 13 supports the 5G network offering faster internet speeds. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The newly launched Apple smartphone has flat-edge aluminium frames with ceramic shield material on the front, and IP68 rating for dust and water protection. IP68 dust and water resistance ratings. The touchscreen display of the phone measures 6.1 inches and has a resolution of 1170 x 2532 pixels at a pixel density of 460 pixels per inch (ppi). Hence, users can enjoy watching videos  and playing games with crystal clear images. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;iPhone 13 is available in different storage variants - 128GB priced at Rs. 79,900, 256GB available at Rs. 89,900 and 512GB costing Rs. 99,900. With such massive storage capacity options, you can store your data and files without any space constraints. Also, you can easily switch between different apps without any lags. In addition to this, the mobile is powered by the A15 Bionic with a four-core GPU that offers faster performance while accessing multiple apps, browsing the web, playing intense graphics games and opening multiple windows on the internet without any lags. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Speaking about the optics, iPhone 13 comes with a dual-camera setup on the rear. There is a 12 MP camera with an f/1.6 aperture and a 12 MP camera with an f/2.4 aperture that has autofocus. On the front, the phone sports a 12 MP camera f/2.2 aperture for making video calls and clicking awesome selfies.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;i