(619, 'Apple iPhone XS', 'apple-phones', 99900, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-65625284,imgsize-400,width-270/65625284.jpg', '&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The latest iPhone XS by renowned brand Apple is all set to hit the market this September. A launch event on Wednesday 12th September is planned, where the brand will be introducing its brand new phone an iPhone XS along with the specifications it will come with. The smartphone will have an edge-to-edge screen with almost a bezel-less screen. iPhone XS Camera will be an improvised version with a TrueDepth camera system that supports Face ID. Designed with most spectacular technology, the latest smartphone by Apple is undeniably the most awaited mobile of the year 2018. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;iPhone XS Price in India&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;iPhone XS Price in India is expected to be approximately Rs. 93,000. The launch of iPhone XS will mark an official end to Home button and the Touch ID fingerprint sensor in Apple\'s flagship iPhone line-up. Apple presents the most elegant iPhone XS with better camera quality, efficient battery backup, remarkable speakers, water resistant and splash proof display and much more.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;iPhone XS Specifications&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;Operating System and Performance&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;: iPhone XS functions on the powerful A12 processor, improved LTE chips from Intel (OLED models only) that will support a faster LTE connection. It is power-driven by Hexa Core (2.35 GHz, Dual-core, Monsoon + 1.42 GHz, Quad core, Mistral) processor along with a RAM of 4 GB. This iPhone is expected to include an improvised USB-C to a lightning cable that ensures faster charging.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;Stunning iPhone XS Cameras - 13MP Plus 8MP Resolutions&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;: One of the most awaited phones of the year 2018, iPhone XS has a rear-facing camera accompanies with a triple-lens array. This time Apple has improvised the rear zoom capacity and picture quality of iPhone XS camera in dim light environments. It is equipped with a 13 MP rear camera and 8 MP front-facing camera with retina flash for wonderful selfies, portrait pictures with an image resolution of 4128 x 3096 Pixels, and HD videos. Settings include exposure compensation, ISO control, Face detection, Touch to focus. There are Continues Shooting, High Dynamic Range (HDR) Modes as well in the smartphone that ensures a picture-perfect experience. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;Beautiful Display &amp; Design with Eye Care Feature&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;: Packed in a stunning curved design, the latest iPhone XS has a 5.8&amp;quot; (14.73 cm) LCD display with a screen resolution of 1125 x 2436 pixels. Boasting a sleek and rich design, iPhone XS is water resistant and dustproof with OLED Display having an aspect ratio of 18:9, and a pixel density of 463 PPI. Its 3D Touch ensures a much smoother &amp; efficient functioning whilst instantly respond to even a subtle touch. The smartphone will be available in two marvellous colours i.e. Gold and Silver.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;Consistent Battery and Storage&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;: Use More, Play more minus any uncertainties of the phone running out of battery. The all new iPhone XS comes with a non-removable Li-ion powerful battery of 2915 mAh capacity, which can proficiently last up to long hours on standard usage with quick charging. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;These days, storage has become a vital specification in a smartphone. The iPhone XS provides ample space to store all your data including high-definition photos, music, HD videos, applications, etc.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Experience world in the palm of your hand with sufficient space in your smartphone.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;Apple iPhone XS Price in India&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;mb20&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Apple iPhone XS smartphone price in India is  Rs 62,999. Apple iPhone XS was launched in the country on September 28, 2018 (Official).The smartphone comes in 2 other storage and RAM variants - Apple iPhone XS 256GB, Apple iPhone XS 512GB. As for the colour options, the Apple iPhone XS smartphone comes in Gold, Silver, Space Grey colours.&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '[]', 1, 0, 'apple-iphone-xs', 'off', '&quot;&quot;', '&quot;&quot;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-05 23:14:29'),
(620, 'Apple iPhone 13 Pro', 'apple-phones', 119900, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-79729964,imgsize-400,width-270/79729964.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;iPhone 13 Pro is one of the newly launched phones amongst iPhone 13 series. The mobile is available in Graphite, Gold, Silver, Sierra Blue color variants at a starting price of Rs 1,19,900. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The newly launched Apple phone has a stainless steel design with a ceramic shield front and a textured matt glass back. It features a 6.1 inches OLED display with a screen resolution of 2532 x 1170 pixels that gives an immersive viewing experience while playing games, recording videos, or watching videos. In addition to this, the mobile is splash, water and dust resistant.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can capture some stunning pictures and videos with the iPhone 13 Pro as it comes with a triple camera setup on the rear. There is a 12 MP primary camera with f/1.5 aperture, a 12 MP ultra wide angle camera with f/1.8 aperture, and a 12 MP camera with f/2.8 aperture. Apart from this, the Apple mobile on the front sports a 12 MP primary camera with f/2.2 aperture for clicking amazing selfies and making video calls.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The mobile from Apple is powered by a hexa-core Apple A15 Bionic processor offering a lightning speed and letting you access multiple apps simultaneously, browse the web, and play intense graphics games without any interruptions. In addition to this, you can buy iPhone 13 Pro in different storage variants - 128GB, 256GB, 512GB, and 1TB that are priced Rs 1,19,900, Rs 1,29,900, Rs 1,49,900, and Rs 1,69,900 respectively.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;iPhone 13 Pro houses a powerful lithium?ion battery that supports fast charging and wireless charging technology. Therefore, you don’t have to worry 