(622, 'Apple iPhone 11 128GB', 'apple-phones', 69900, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-71078790,imgsize-400,width-270/71078790.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;Buy the Apple iPhone 11 128GB, which not just has pleasant looks but is also equipped with striking features. The mobile phone was launched in India on September 20, 2019 (Official) at a starting price of Rs 69,900.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;This Apple phone is powerful to the core as it lets you enjoy a breezy-smooth performance while accessing multiple apps since it is powered with Hexa Core (2.65 GHz, Dual core, Lightning + 1.8 GHz, Quad core, Thunder) Apple A13 Bionic. Moreover, the phone comes with 4 GB of RAM and 128 GB of internal storage so that you can store all your songs, videos, games, pictures and other stuff without worrying about space constraints.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The &amp;lt;a href=https://www.gadgetsnow.com/mobile-phones&amp;gt;mobile&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; paves the way for crystal clear visuals as it comes with a 6.1 inches (15.49 cm) display that has a resolution of 828 x 1792 pixels..&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Furthermore, the aspect ratio of the Apple iPhone 11 128GB is 19.5:9 so that you can enjoy vivid and crystal clear visuals while watching videos, playing games, or streaming movies online..&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The camera specifications of the phone are very captivating. The Apple iPhone 11 128GB comes with a Single camera setup on the rear which has 12 MP + 12 MP cameras so that you can capture portraits, landscapes, and more in the form of beautiful pictures. Features on the rear camera setup include 5 x Digital Zoom, 2 x Optical Zoom, Auto Flash, Face detection, Touch to focus. On the front, the mobile features a 12 MP camera so that you can click some amazing selfies and do video chats.&amp;lt;br/&am