(623, 'Oneplus Nord CE 5G', 'one-plus-phones', 22999, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-82932013,imgsize-400,width-270/82932013.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;OnePlus, the Chinese smartphone company, has launched the OnePlus Nord CE 5G smartphone at a starting price of Rs 22,999. This newly launched budget smartphone is available in Charcoal Ink, Silver Ray, and Blue Void color options. The impressive features and decent specifications of the mobile make it highly popular amongst users. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;This new entrant in the OnePlus family comes with a 6.43 inches Fluid AMOLED display that has a resolution of 1080 x 2400 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9 that will offer you an exceptional experience while watching videos or playing games on it. Furthermore, this dual-SIM phone is powered by a Li-Polymer 4500mAh non-removable battery with Warp Charge 30T Plus fast charging support. Hence, you will have to worry about charging your phone frequently or its battery drainage while you are in the middle of a call, playing a game or attending an online class. Also, the smartphone runs the OxygenOS based on the Android 11 operating system offering you a clutter free and user-friendly user interface. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;This newly launched &amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://www.gadgetsnow.com/mobile-phones/OnePlus&amp;quot;&amp;gt;mobile from OnePlus&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt; comes with a triple camera setup on the rear for clicking awesome pictures and recording high quality videos. There is a 64 MP primary camera with f/1.79 aperture, an 8 MP ultra wide angle camera with f/2.25 aperture, and a 2 MP mono lens with f/2.4 aperture. Features on the rear setup camera include Panorama, Digital Zoom, LED Flash, Autofocus, UltraShot HDR, Portrait, Nightscape, Smart scene recognition, Pro mode, Filters, and more. While on the front, the phone sports a 16 MP camera with f/2.45 aperture for taking selfies and making video calls. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Apart from this, the OnePlus Nord CE 5G is equipped with Octa core (2.2 GHz, Dual core, Kryo 570 + 1.8 GHz, Hexa Core, Kryo 570) Qualcomm Snapdragon 750G processor so that you can enjoy an uninterrupted and faster performance while accessing multiple apps or playing intense graphics games. Furthermore, the phone comes in three storage variants - 8GB of RAM + 128GB of internal storage, 6GB of RAM + 128GB of internal storage, and 12GB of RAM + 256GB of internal storage thus offering you an amazing speed. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Sensors on the OnePlus Nord CE 5G include an in-display fingerprint sensor, accelerometer, electronic compass, gyroscope, ambient light sensor, proximity sensor, and sensor core. Besides, connectivity options on the phone include 5G supported by device (network not rolled-out in India), 4G (supports Indian bands), 3G, 2G, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, 2.4G/5G, Bluetooth 5.1, NFC, GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, Beidou, A-GPS, NaVIC, and more.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h6&amp;gt;Oneplus Nord CE 5G Price In India&amp;lt;/h6&amp;gt;Oneplus Nord CE 5G smartphone price in India is Rs 24,999. Oneplus Nord CE 5G was launched in the country on June 10, 2021 (Official). Thesmartphone comes in 2 other storage and RAM variants - Oneplus-Nord-CE-5G-128GB-8GB-RAM, Oneplus-Nord-CE-5G-256GB-12GB-RAM. As for the colour options, the Oneplus Nord CE 5G smartphone comes in Charcoal Ink, Blue Void, Silver Ray colours.&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '{\"general_\":{\"0\":\"\",\"launch date\":\"June 10, 2021 (Official)\",\"price in india\":\"22999\",\"brand\":\"OnePlus\",\"model\":\"Nord CE 5G\",\"operating system\":\"Android v11\",\"custom ui\":\"OxygenOS\",\"sim