(631, 'OnePlus 7T', 'one-plus-phones', 37999, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-70856607,imgsize-400,width-270/70856607.jpg', '&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Launched in September 2019, OnePlus 7T is a decent and mid-range smartphone from the brand that comes with striking features and specifications. The smartphone comes with a combination of metal and frosted glass that sets it apart from various other devices. The phone features a 6.55 inches fluid display with a resolution of 1080x2400 pixels that offers an incredibly immersive viewing experience. It has an aspect ratio of 20:9 and 90Hz refresh rate. Also, the phone comes with Gorilla Glass 5 protection on both front and back. Apart from this, the dimensions of the phone are 160.9 mm x 74.4 mm x 8.1 mm (HXWXD), and it weighs around 190 grams. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The OnePlus 7T phone is equipped with the Qualcomm Snapdragon 855 Plus processor that provides you a lag-free performance. And, it is available in 8GB RAM + 128GB internal storage and 8GB RAM + 256GB internal storage variants. In addition to this, the smartphone comes with OxygenOS 10.0.7, based on Android 10.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can click some stunning pictures from OnePlus 7T. On the rear, it features a 48 MP primary camera with f/1.6 aperture, a 12 MP telephoto camera with f/2.2 aperture, and a 16 MP ultrawide angle camera with f/2.2 aperture. Also, it comprises dual-LED flash, HDR, and panorama features. While on the front, the mobile comes with a 16 MP camera with an Auto-HDR feature.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can enjoy watching movies, browsing the internet, and playing games on OnePlus 7T without worrying about battery drainage as it houses a 3800 mAh non-removable battery with Warp Charge 30T that supports fast charging. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Apart from this, various connectivity options on the smartphone include &amp;lt;br/&amp;gt; Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot, Bluetooth, GPS, NFC, Radio, reversible connector, and USB On-The-Go. Moreover, sensors on the OnePlus 7T are an accelerometer, electronic compass, gyroscope, in-display fingerprint sensor, ambient light sensor, sensor core, and proximity sensor.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can buy OnePlus 7T in Glacier Blue?and Frosted Silver color options.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;OnePlus 7T Price in India&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;mb20&amp;quot;&amp;gt;OnePlus 7T smartphone price in India is  Rs 30,550. OnePlus 7T was launched in the country on September 28, 2019 (Official).The smartphone comes in 1 other storage and RAM variants - OnePlus 7T 256GB. As for the colour options, the OnePlus 7T smartphone comes in  Frosted Silver, Glacier Blue colours.&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '[]', 1, 0, 'oneplus-7t', 'off', '&quot;&quot;', '&quot;&quot;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-05 23:23:31'),
(632, 'OnePlus 7', 'one-plus-phones', 32999, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-78559971,imgsize-400,width-270/78559971.jpg', 'OnePlus 7 was launched in India on June 1, 2019 (Official) at an introductory price of Rs 32,999 and is available in different color options like Red, Mirror Grey. In addition to this, the mobile measures 157.7 mm x 74.8 mm x 8.2 mm; and weighs around 182 grams. The mobile from OnePlus features 6.41 inches (16.28 cm) display that has a resolution of 1080 x 2340 pixels.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Furthermore, the aspect ratio of the OnePlus 7 is 19.5:9 so that you can enjoy vivid and crystal clear visuals while watching videos, playing games, or streaming movies online..&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;You can enjoy seamless performance on your phone as it is equipped with Octa core (2.84 GHz, Single core, Kryo 485 + 2.42 GHz, Tri core, Kryo 485 + 1.8 GHz, Quad core, Kryo 485) Qualcomm Snapdragon 855. The phone comes with 6 GB and 128 GB inbuilt storage so that you can store your local files, songs, videos and more without worrying about space constraints. Besides, the OnePlus 7 runs Android v9.0 (Pie) operating system and is packed with 3700 mAh battery that lets you enjoy watching movies, playing games and do a lot more without worrying about battery drainage.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;The camera of the OnePlus 7 comes with Single camera setup on the rear which has 48 MP + 5 MP cameras. While on the front, the mobile sports a 16 MP front camera so that you can click some amazing selfies.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;Various connectivity options on the OnePlus 7 include WiFi - Yes Wi-Fi 802.11, a/ac/b/g/n/n 5GHz, MIMO, Mobile Hotspot, Bluetooth - Yes v5.0, and 4G (supports Indian bands), 3G, 2G. Sensors on the mobile include Light sensor, Proximity sensor, Accelerometer, Compass, Gyroscope.&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;OnePlus 7 Price in India&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;mb20&amp;quot;&amp;gt;OnePlus 7 smartphone price in India is  Rs 26,398. OnePlus 7 was launched in the country on June 1, 2019 (Official).The smartphone comes in 1 other storage and RAM variants - OnePlus 7 256GB. As for the colour options, the OnePlus 7 smartphone comes in Red, Mirror Grey colours.&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '[]', 1, 0, 'oneplus-7', 'off', '&quot;&quot;', '&quot;&quot;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-05 23:23:32'),
