(637, 'OPPO A5 2020', 'oppo-phones', 12990, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-70995876,imgsize-400,width-270/70995876.jpg', '&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The Oppo A5 (2020) smartphone was launched alongside the Oppo A9 (2020) and was also made available in two RAM and internal storage variants: 3GB+64GB and 4GB+128GB. The 3GB+64GB model was priced at Rs 12,490 while the 4GB+128GB variant was priced at Rs 13,990. These smartphone was made available in two colour options: Dazzling White and Mirror Black. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The dimensions of the smartphone are 163.6mm x 75.6mm x 9.1mm (L x W x D) and weighs about 195gm.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Oppo A5 (2020) features a 6.5-inch multi-touch, capacitive touchscreen display with a resolution of 1600 by 720 pixels.The device supports 16 million colours. It has a screen ratio of 89.0 percent and a contrast ratio of 1500:1.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt; The smartphone runs ColorOS 6.0.1 based on Android 9 and is powered by Qualcomm Snapdragon 665 processor and Adreno 610 GPU. The device comes in two LPDDR 4x RAM options: 3GB and 4GB. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Coming to the optics, the phone comes equipped with a quad rear camera setup of 12MP + 8MP + 2MP +2MP sensors. The main 12MP sensor comes with f/1.8 aperture, the 8MP sensor comes with f/2.25 aperture, and both the 2MP sensors have f/2.4 aperture each. The front camera is an 8MP one with an aperture of f/2.0.  The rear camera supports video recording up to 4K@30fps, 1080P@30fps and 720P@30fps while the front camera is capable of video recording in 1080P/720P@30fps.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The various sensors that the phone comes with are geomagnetic sensor, proximity sensor, light sensor, acceleration sensor, gravity sensor and a gyro sensor.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;It is backed by a huge 5000mAh battery. There are two native internal storage options that the phone comes in: 64GB and 128GB.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2&amp;gt;OPPO A5 2020 Price in India&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;mb20&amp;quot;&amp;gt;OPPO A5 2020 smartphone price in India is  Rs 12,990. OPPO A5 2020 was launched in the country on October 1, 2019 (Official).The smartphone comes in 2 other storage and RAM variants - OPPO A5 2020 4GB RAM, OPPO A5 2020 128GB. As for the colour options, the OPPO A5 2020 smartphone comes in  Mirror Black, Dazzling White colours.&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '[]', 1, 0, 'oppo-a5-2020', 'off', '&quot;&quot;', '&quot;&quot;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-05 23:43:34'),
