(639, 'Oppo Reno 6 5G', 'oppo-phones', 29990, 0, 'https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-82089434,imgsize-400,width-270/82089434.jpg', '&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Oppo, one of the leading mobile brands, has launched Oppo Reno 6 5G and Oppo Reno 6 Pro 5G in India. Both the smartphones come with striking features and adequate specifications. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Oppo Reno 6 5G is a dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by) mobile that is priced at Rs. 29,990. The ultra-slim retro design, which is sleek and has flat-edged middle frame construction offers you comfortable usage. The dimensions of the mobile are 156.8 mm x 72.1 mm x 7.59 mm (height x width x thickness) and weighs approximately 182 grams. Furthermore, the phone can be bought in Stellar Black and Aurora color options.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You get to experience an immersive viewing experience at the time of watching videos or playing games as the phone comes with a 6.43 inches flat AMOLED display that has a resolution of 1080 x 2400 pixels, 90Hz refresh rate, and 91.7% screen-to-body ratio.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Oppo Reno 6 5G, the newly launched mobile, is equipped with Octa-core (2x2.4 GHz Cortex-A78 &amp; 6x2.0 GHz Cortex-A55) MediaTek MT6877 Dimensity 900 5G (6 nm) processor for enjoying a speedy and lag-free performance while accessing multiple applications simultaneously, browsing the web, and playing games. Also, the mobile comes with 8 GB of RAM and 128 GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 2 TB for easily storing your files like pictures, apps, videos, songs, and more without any space restrictions.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The triple rear camera setup on the mobile lets you capture high resolution images and videos. There is a 64 MP primary camera with f/1.7 aperture, an 8 MP ultra wide angle camera with f/2.2 aperture, and a 2 MP macro sensor with  f/2.4 aperture. Features on the rear camera setup include HDR, panorama, LED flash, and more. On the front, the phone sports a 32 MP camera with f/2.4 aperture for selfies and video calls. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Oppo Reno 6 5G gives you a clutter-free and user-friendly UI as it runs ColorOS 11.3 based on the Android 11 operating system. Furthermore, the smartphone houses a Li-Po 4300 mAh non-removable battery that supports 65W SuperVOOC 2.0 fast charging. There will be zero worries of frequently charging the phone or battery drainage while you are making a call, playing a game, attending online classes, clicking pictures, and more&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;There are different connectivity options that include on Oppo Reno 6 5G such as 5G supported by device (network not rolled-out in India), 4G (supports Indian bands), 3G, 2G, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac/6, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot, GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS, GALILEO, QZSS, Bluetooth, USB Type-C 3.1, and more. Sensors on the mobile include proximity sensor, fingerprint sensor, gyro, colour temperature sensor, accelerometer, and compass.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h6&amp;gt;Oppo Reno 6 5G Price In India&amp;lt;/h6&amp;gt;Oppo Reno 6 5G smartphone price in India is Rs 28,490. Oppo Reno 6 5G was launched in the country on July 14, 2021 (Official). As for the colour options, the Oppo Reno 6 5G smartphone comes in Aurora, Stellar Black colours.&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '', '{\"general_\":{\"0\":\"\",\"launch date\":\"July 14, 2021 (Official)\",\"price in india\":\"29990\",\"brand\":\"OPPO\",\"model\":\"Reno 6 5G\",\"operating system\":\"Android v11\",\"sim slots\":\"Dual SIM, GSM+GSM\",\"sim size\":\"SIM1: Nano, SIM2: Nano\",\"network\":\"5G supported by device (network not rolled-out in India), 4G (su