(708, 'Micromax IN 1b', 'micromax-phones', 8999, 0, '/Public/asset/images/2022/69b7915ebfcb66958875df2cab.jpeg', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;lIZA8&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;height:auto&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Buy the brand new Micromax In 1b smartphone that was launched in India on November 03, 2020. In this dual-SIM (GSM and GSM) mobile both Nano-SIM and Nano-SIM cards can be inserted. Measuring around 164.50 mm x 75.80 mm x 8.90 mm (height x width x thickness) and weighing around 188 grams, the Micromax In 1b is easy to carry and use.&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can have an immersive viewing experience as the Micromax In 1b comes with a 6.52-inch IPS LCD touchscreen display that has a resolution of 720x1600 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9. Apart from this, the smartphone offers you a smooth and lag-free performance as it is equipped with an octa-core MediaTek Helio G35 processor. Also, you can access multiple apps at the same time without any interruption.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;The smartphone from Micromax is based on the Android 10 operating system and comes with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of inbuilt storage. Also, you can expand the inbuilt storage of your phone up to 128GB using a microSD card with a dedicated slot so that you can store all your local files like songs, games, videos, pictures, and more without worrying about space constraints.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Apart from this, the Micromax In 1b mobile is powered by a massive 5000mAh non-removable battery that supports proprietary fast charging and lets you use the phone for a longer period of time without worrying about battery draining.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Speaking about the optics of Micromax In 1b, you get a dual-camera setup on the rear. There is a 13 MP primary camera with f/1.8 aperture and a 2 MP depth sensor with f/2.4 aperture. Also, the rear camera setup has an LED flash and autofocus. While on the front, there is an 8 MP camera for video chats and selfies.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;There are various connectivity options on the Micromax In 1b such as 3.5mm jack, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot, Bluetooth v5.00, USB Type-C, GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, 3G, and 4G (with support for Band 40 used by some LTE networks in India). Sensors on the mobile include a fingerprint sensor, ambient light sensor, accelerometer, proximity sensor, and gyroscope.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;You can buy the Micromax In 1b in Green, Purple, and Blue colors at a starting price of Rs. 6,999.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h3&amp;gt;&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;Micromax In 1B Key Features&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/h3&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Micromax In 1b has a 6.52-inch display and 720x1600 pixels resolution&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Dual camera setup on the rear comes with features like LED flash and autofocus&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Front camera is of 8 MP&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Powered by 5000mAh non-removable battery&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Runs Android 10 OS and equipped with octa-core MediaTek Helio G35 processor&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;2GB RAM and 32GB inbuilt storage&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Dimensions of the phone are 164.50 mm x 75.80 mm x 8.90 mm; weight is 188 grams&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li&amp;gt;Color options: Green, Purple and Blue&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h6&amp;gt;Micromax IN 1b Price In India&amp;lt;/h6&amp;gt;Micromax IN 1b smartphone price in India is Rs 8,900. Micromax IN 1b was launched in the country on November 3, 2020 (Official). Thesmartphone comes in 1 other storage and RAM variants - Micromax-IN-1b-64GB-4GB-RAM. As for the colour options, the Micromax IN 1b smartphone comes in Blue, Green, Purple colours.&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'You can have an immersive viewing experience as the Micromax In 1b comes with a 6.52-inch IPS LCD touchscreen display that has a resolution of 720x1600 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9. Apart from this, the smartphone offers you a smooth and lag-free performance as it is equipped with an octa-core MediaTek Helio G35 processor. Also, you can access multiple apps at the same time without any interruption', '{', 1, 0, 'micromax-in-1b', 'off', '{&quot;general_launch_date&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;general_price_in_india&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;general_model&quot;:&quot;&quot;}', '{&quot;design_height&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;design_width&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;design_thickness&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;design_weight&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;design_colours&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;design_water_proof&quot;:&quot;&quot;}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-02-19 10:23:07'),
