(761, 'Oppo K10 5G', 'one-plus-phones', 903, 1, '/Public/asset/images/2022/69b7915ebfcb66958875df2cab.jpeg', '&lt;h2&gt;ppo K10 5G Summary&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Oppo K10 5G mobile was launched on 24th April 2022. The phone comes with a 120 Hz refresh rate 6.59-inch touchscreen display offering a resolution of 1080x2412 pixels (FHD+) at a pixel density of 401 pixels per inch (ppi). Oppo K10 5G is powered by an octa-core MediaTek Dimensity 8000-Max processor. It comes with 8GB, 12GB of RAM. The Oppo K10 5G runs Android 12 and is powered by a 5000mAh non-removable battery. The Oppo K10 5G supports Super VOOC fast charging.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As far as the cameras are concerned, the Oppo K10 5G on the rear packs a triple camera setup featuring a 64-megapixel (f/1.8) primary camera; an 8-megapixel (f/2.2) camera, and a 2-megapixel (f/2.4) camera. The rear camera setup has autofocus. It has a single front camera setup for selfies, featuring a 16-megapixel sensor with an f/2.05 aperture.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Oppo K10 5G runs ColorOS 12.1 is based on Android 12 and packs 128GB, 256GB of inbuilt storage. The Oppo K10 5G is a dual-SIM mobile. The Oppo K10 5G measures 164.30 x 75.80 x 8.73mm (height x width x thickness) and weighs 205.00 grams. It was launched in Black and Blue colours.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Connectivity options on the Oppo K10 5G include Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, GPS, Bluetooth v5.30, NFC, and USB Type-C. Sensors on the phone include accelerometer, ambient light sensor, gyroscope, proximity sensor, and fingerprint sensor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As of 3rd July 2022, Oppo K10 5G price in India starts at Rs. 17,499.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Oppo K10 5G mobile was launched on 24th April 2022. The phone comes with a 120 Hz refresh rate 6.59-inch touchscreen display offering a resolution of 1080x2412 pixels (FHD+) at a pixel density of 401 pixels per inch (ppi). Oppo K10 5G is powered by an octa-core MediaTek Dimensity 8000-Max processor. It comes with 8GB, 12GB of RAM. The Oppo K10 5G runs Android 12 and is powered by a 5000mAh non-removable battery. The Oppo K10 5G supports Super VOOC fast charging.', '{\"key_specs\":{\"0\":\"Key Specs\",\"Ram\":\"100 GB\",\"Processor\":\"MediaTek Dimensity 8000-Max\",\"Rear Camera\":\"64MP + 8MP + 2MP\",\"os\":\"Android 12\",\"battery capacity\":\"5000Mah\",\"Brand\":\"Oppo\",\"Model\":\"K10 5G\",\"form factor\":\"Touchscreen\",\"Launch Date\":\"24th April 2022\"},\"general\":{\"Screen Size\":\"6.59\",\"Screen Resolution\":\"1080x2412 pixels\",\"Touch Screen\":\"Yes\",\"Screen Protection\":\"Yes\"},\"display\":{\"Camera Features\":\"64-megapixel (f\\/1.8) + 8-megapixel (f\\/2.2) + 2-megapixel (f\\/2.4)\",\"Autofocus\":\"Yes\",\"Flash\":\"Yes\"},\"camera\":{\" fingerprint sensor\":\"Yes\",\"proximity sensor\":\"yes\",\"accelerometer\":\"Yes\",\"ambient light sensor\":\"Yes\",\"gyroscope\":\"Yes\"}}', 1, 8, 'oppo-k10-5g', 'off', '&quot;&quot;', '&quot;&quot;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-07-03 19:08:21'),
